imdb.plot outline: The series is set in the fictional world of Novoland and tells the story of loyalty, friendship, enmity, struggles and romance between the young descendants during the twilight years of the Duan Dynasty: a half-spirit prince, son of a general, a tribesman leader, a girl with Queen fate, a spirit woman, a warrior princess.
